{"type":"weapons","title":"Magic Missile","summaries":["The <b>Magic Missile</b> is a <linked>magic weapon</linked> that can be found in the <linked>Dungeon</linked>'s locked <linked>Gold Chests</linked>. It can also be found in <span class=\"eil\"><span><linked>Golden Lock Boxes</linked></span><span class=\"eico s i1 i2 i4 i6\" title=\"Desktop, Console, Mobile and Legacy tModLoader versions\"><b></b><i></i></span></span> found in <span class=\"eil\"><span><linked>Dungeon</linked></span><span class=\"eico s i1 i2 i4 i6\" title=\"Desktop, Console, Mobile and Legacy tModLoader versions\"><b></b><i></i></span></span> and <span class=\"eil\"><span><linked>Stockade Crates</linked></span><span class=\"eico s i1 i2 i4\" title=\"Desktop, Console and Mobile versions\"><b></b><i></i></span></span> which are fished up in the Dungeon. It fires an exploding projectile that can be controlled by holding the <span class=\"key\"><linked>⚒ Use / Attack</linked></span> button and moving the cursor. If the <span class=\"key\"><linked>⚒ Use / Attack</linked></span> button is released mid-drag, the missile will be flung in that direction. If the cursor is stationary on release, it flies directly away from the player. The projectile also emits a moderate amount of light.","<span class=\"eico i1 i2 i4\" title=\"Desktop, Console and Mobile versions\"><b></b><i></i></span> If any enemies are nearby when the missile is released, the missile will home in and attack them.","Its best <linked>modifier</linked> is <b>Mythical</b>."],"statistics":{"Damage":"35 <span class=\"eico s i1 i2 i4\" title=\"Desktop, Console and Mobile versions\"><b></b><i></i></span> / 27 <span class=\"eico s i6\" title=\"Legacy tModLoader version\"><b></b><i></i></span> / 23 <span class=\"eico s i3 i5\" title=\"Old-gen console and 3DS versions\"><b></b><i></i></span> <span class=\"small-bold\">(Magic)</span>","Knockback":"7.5 <span class=\"knockback\">(Very strong)</span> <span class=\"eico s i1 i2 i4 i6\" title=\"Desktop, Console, Mobile and Legacy tModLoader versions\"><b></b><i></i></span> /<br> 5.5 <span class=\"knockback\">(Average)</span> <span class=\"eico s i3 i5\" title=\"Old-gen console and 3DS versions\"><b></b><i></i></span>","Mana":"14 <span class=\"eico s i1 i2 i4\" title=\"Desktop, Console and Mobile versions\"><b></b><i></i></span> / 10 <span class=\"eico s i3 i5 i6\" title=\"Old-gen console, 3DS and Legacy tModLoader versions\"><b></b><i></i></span>","Critical chance":"4%","Use time":"22 <span class=\"usetime\">(Fast)</span> <span class=\"eico s i1 i2 i4\" title=\"Desktop, Console and Mobile versions\"><b></b><i></i></span> /<br> 17 <span class=\"usetime\">(Very fast)</span> <span class=\"eico s i3 i5 i6\" title=\"Old-gen console, 3DS and Legacy tModLoader versions\"><b></b><i></i></span>","Velocity":"6","Tooltip":"<i><span class=\"gameText\">Casts a controllable missile</span></i>","Rarity":"<span class=\"rarity\"><linked>[img:Rarity level: 2]</linked></span>","Sell":"<span class=\"coin\" title=\"1 Gold 75 Silver Coins\" data-sort-value=\"17500\"><span class=\"gc\">1</span><span class=\"sc\">75</span></span>","Research":"<abbr class=\"journey\" title=\"Journey Mode\">1 required</abbr>"},"crafts":{"Used in":[{"result":{"rowspan":1,"value":"<span class=\"i multi-line\"><linked>[img:Sky Fracture]</linked><span><span><linked>Sky Fracture</linked></span><span class=\"eico s i1 i2 i4 i6\" title=\"Desktop, Console, Mobile and Legacy tModLoader versions\"><b></b><i></i></span></span></span>"},"ingredients":{"value":"<ul><li><span class=\"i\"><linked>[img:Magic Missile]</linked><span><span><linked>Magic Missile</linked></span></span></span></li><li><span class=\"i\"><linked>[img:Light Shard]</linked><span><span><linked>Light Shard</linked></span></span></span> <span class=\"note-text\">(2)</span></li><li><span class=\"i\"><linked>[img:Soul of Light]</linked><span><span><linked>Soul of Light</linked></span></span></span> <span class=\"note-text\">(16)</span></li></ul>"},"sta